<item><title>过去一周三名阿拉伯裔以色列妇女被谋杀：“警察袖手旁观”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/three-arab-israeli-women-murdered-over-past-week-the-police-stands-idle/00000191-ad66-d3dd-a991-ad7ee92b0000</link><description>据《国土报》数据，今年以来，以色列各地已有20名女性在各类事件中被谋杀，其中7名来自阿拉伯社区</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 14:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/three-arab-israeli-women-murdered-over-past-week-the-police-stands-idle/00000191-ad66-d3dd-a991-ad7ee92b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列体育俱乐部在为球迷赫什·戈德堡-波林从哈马斯的囚禁中获释而奋斗后告别了他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/sports-club-bids-farewell-to-hersh-goldberg-polin-after-fighting-to-release-him-from-gaza/00000191-adc6-dd1e-adb5-afce5a710000</link><description>这位出生于加利福尼亚州的 23 岁以色列裔美国人是耶路撒冷夏普尔足球队和篮球队的忠实粉丝。在他最黑暗的时刻，俱乐部和球迷从未忘记他</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 14:24:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/sports-club-bids-farewell-to-hersh-goldberg-polin-after-fighting-to-release-him-from-gaza/00000191-adc6-dd1e-adb5-afce5a710000</guid></item><item><title>加沙和约旦河西岸之间的“战线统一”似乎比以往任何时候都更加紧密</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/a-unity-of-fronts-between-gaza-and-west-bank-seems-closer-than-ever/00000191-aceb-d4e9-a199-acef1aba0000</link><description>定居者在西岸对巴勒斯坦人实施的持续暴力行为，以及本格维尔在圣殿山的挑衅，可能导致西岸暴力爆发</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 12:40:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/a-unity-of-fronts-between-gaza-and-west-bank-seems-closer-than-ever/00000191-aceb-d4e9-a199-acef1aba0000</guid></item><item><title>从加沙打捞出六名人质尸体后，以色列劳工联合会主席宣布大罢工</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/businesses-across-israel-to-close-early-ahead-of-mass-rally-for-hostage-deal/00000191-ad7a-d95c-a5b5-ff7bc4960000</link><description>由于全国范围内的大罢工，以色列国际机场将于周一上午 8 点开始暂停运营。餐馆、电影院和其他场所将在周日晚上提前关闭，以支持计划在特拉维夫举行的大规模集会</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 12:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/businesses-across-israel-to-close-early-ahead-of-mass-rally-for-hostage-deal/00000191-ad7a-d95c-a5b5-ff7bc4960000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部的父母被迫在孩子的安全和教育之间做出选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/parents-in-northern-israel-forced-to-choose-between-childrens-safety-and-education/00000191-aa21-d2ec-a1f7-ef7178810000</link><description>在黎巴嫩近十一个月的持续轰炸中，政府未能找到解决受到威胁的道路和保护不足的教室的解决方案</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 12:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/parents-in-northern-israel-forced-to-choose-between-childrens-safety-and-education/00000191-aa21-d2ec-a1f7-ef7178810000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质死亡，内塔尼亚胡可以让他的联盟继续存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-finally-condemned-the-israeli-hostages-to-their-deaths-in-gaza/00000191-ad36-d4e9-a199-ad771b570000</link><description>出于政治考虑和军事压力而放弃被囚禁的以色列人，巩固了总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡作为独裁者的遗产，他显然对自己的公民没有任何责任感</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 11:56:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-finally-condemned-the-israeli-hostages-to-their-deaths-in-gaza/00000191-ad36-d4e9-a199-ad771b570000</guid></item><item><title>在火人节上，哈马斯在以色列新星节大屠杀中的“天使”复活了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-burning-man-angels-from-israels-nova-festival-come-back-to-life/00000191-ad2a-d453-ab9f-fdae2f6d0000</link><description>在内华达州沙漠举行的音乐节上，10 月 7 日加沙边境附近狂欢的幸存者搭建了“新星天堂”装置，向被哈马斯杀害的音乐节观众致敬</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 11:53:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-burning-man-angels-from-israels-nova-festival-come-back-to-life/00000191-ad2a-d453-ab9f-fdae2f6d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡知道以色列人质的时间已经不多了。他的手上沾满了他们的血”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-knew-the-israeli-hostages-were-on-borrowed-time-their-blood-is-on-his-hands/00000191-acf1-d453-ab9f-fcfd1a3b0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政府的一名高级成员接着说，“每个人都知道他是一个自恋者和胆小鬼”。但他的缺乏人性在最近几个月里得到了充分、丑陋的体现。</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 11:29:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-knew-the-israeli-hostages-were-on-borrowed-time-their-blood-is-on-his-hands/00000191-acf1-d453-ab9f-fcfd1a3b0000</guid></item><item><title>美国、以色列和哈马斯调解员对内塔尼亚胡总理对加沙协议的意图失去了信心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/u-s-israel-hamas-mediators-have-lost-faith-in-netanyahu-pms-intentions-for-gaza-deal/00000191-acb5-d4e9-a199-acf502c00000</link><description>一名以色列官员补充说，内塔尼亚胡一直在停火和人质协议谈判中提出“一个又一个障碍”。以色列国防军周日从加沙打捞出六名人质尸体后，尚不清楚谈判是否会加快或一劳永逸地掩埋</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 09:20:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/u-s-israel-hamas-mediators-have-lost-faith-in-netanyahu-pms-intentions-for-gaza-deal/00000191-acb5-d4e9-a199-acf502c00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：那些谋杀人质的人不想达成协议；甘茨呼吁抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-those-who-murder-hostages-dont-want-a-deal-gantz-calls-for-protests/00000191-ac63-d172-abd9-eef72c6e0000</link><description>以色列国防军从加沙打捞出六名人质尸体后，以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡发表了一份录音声明。声明发表后，人质论坛呼吁总理对“遗弃”人质“承担责任”</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 08:33:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-those-who-murder-hostages-dont-want-a-deal-gantz-calls-for-protests/00000191-ac63-d172-abd9-eef72c6e0000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列警察在约旦河西岸枪击事件中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/three-police-officers-killed-in-west-bank-shooting/00000191-ac42-d453-ab9f-fccee5b00000</link><description>以色列军队正在寻找在塔尔库米亚检查站附近射杀一辆载有国防人员的车辆的几名嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 07:07:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/three-police-officers-killed-in-west-bank-shooting/00000191-ac42-d453-ab9f-fccee5b00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队找到了最近被哈马斯处决的六名人质的尸体，这些人质被绑架到加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-recovers-bodies-of-six-hostages-kidnapped-to-gaza-by-hamas-on-october-7/00000191-abf9-d23c-a1d3-abff44100000</link><description>所有六人都被活活绑架，三人本应在与哈马斯达成协议的第一部分中被释放 ■ 以色列国防军发言人表示，他们是在拉法的一个隧道中被发现的，很可能是在部队抵达“前不久”被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 06:28:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-recovers-bodies-of-six-hostages-kidnapped-to-gaza-by-hamas-on-october-7/00000191-abf9-d23c-a1d3-abff44100000</guid></item><item><title>美国总统拜登对美国裔以色列人赫什·戈德堡-波林在哈马斯囚禁期间死亡感到“震惊和愤怒”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/biden-devastated-and-outraged-over-death-of-hersh-goldberg-polin-in-hamas-captivity/00000191-abe1-dd1e-adb5-abef511c0000</link><description>戈德堡-波林的父母曾多次会见美国官员和其他国际高级领导人，并于最近在民主党全国代表大会上发表讲话。拜登说：“我对他们的钦佩和悲痛之情无法用言语表达。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 05:25:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/biden-devastated-and-outraged-over-death-of-hersh-goldberg-polin-in-hamas-captivity/00000191-abe1-dd1e-adb5-abef511c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军从加沙哈马斯的囚禁中打捞出六名人质的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-live/idf-finds-hostages-bodies-in-gaza-family-of-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin-announces-death/00000191-ab89-d453-ab9f-fb8ddb250000</link><description>卫生部：六名人质遭近距离枪击；估计已于周四或周五被杀 ■ 黎巴嫩报道：以色列在黎巴嫩南部发动袭击 ■ 数十名要求人质交易的抗议者封锁特拉维夫高速公路 ■ 以色列国防军称袭击了哈马斯用作控制中心的加沙城学校 ■ 以色列劳工联合会主席宣布总罢工 ■ 据报道，以色列北部城镇卡法尤瓦尔发射反坦克导弹造成人员伤亡 ■ 三名警察在约旦河西岸枪击事件中丧生</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 03:36:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-live/idf-finds-hostages-bodies-in-gaza-family-of-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin-announces-death/00000191-ab89-d453-ab9f-fb8ddb250000</guid></item><item><title>杰宁居民称他们已被围困多日，基础设施遭到破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/jenin-residents-say-theyve-been-under-siege-for-days-infrastructure-has-been-destroyed/00000191-aa36-d2ec-a1f7-ef76a4be0000</link><description>一名居民表示，停电可能会导致食物变质，居民们都呆在家里。 ■ 该市红新月会主任表示，以色列军方向救护车开枪</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 01:08:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/jenin-residents-say-theyve-been-under-siege-for-days-infrastructure-has-been-destroyed/00000191-aa36-d2ec-a1f7-ef76a4be0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军在加沙地带发现人质尸体；身份识别过程正在进行中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/idf-finds-bodies-of-hostages-in-gaza-strip-identification-process-ongoing/00000191-aa59-d2ec-a1f7-ef79c5300000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布这一消息后，人质和失踪家庭论坛发表声明：“内塔尼亚胡已经抛弃了人质，从明天开始，国家将颤抖”</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 22:42:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/idf-finds-bodies-of-hostages-in-gaza-strip-identification-process-ongoing/00000191-aa59-d2ec-a1f7-ef79c5300000</guid></item><item><title>只有以色列军事压力才能释放人质的说法始终是错误的。现在已经支离破碎了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/the-claim-that-only-military-force-can-free-hostages-was-always-wrong-now-its-shattered/00000191-a9e6-d453-ab9f-f9ee87e90000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在最近一次内阁会议上批准以色列国防军继续在费城航线驻扎，这是一个历史性的低点，即使在当前战争的历史上也是如此。现在很清楚：消灭哈马斯的斗争可能会导致更多人质丧生</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 20:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/the-claim-that-only-military-force-can-free-hostages-was-always-wrong-now-its-shattered/00000191-a9e6-d453-ab9f-f9ee87e90000</guid></item></channel></rss>